data.title: This Is Johan (TV Mini Series 2024)
data.meta_description: This Is Johan: With Joe Flizzow, Aishah Ali, Remus Chang, Wan Marina. Dubbed the Godfather of Malaysian hip-hop, Johan Ishak AKA Joe Flizzow has Havoc the Malaysian music industry from the days of Too Phat to Mr President and this is the story of BikinSampaiJadi an iconic Malaysian rapper.
